data.title: Anti-CRMP4 antibody (ab244319)
data.meta_description: Rabbit Polyclonal CRMP4 antibody. Suitable for IHC-P, WB, ICC/IF and reacts with Human, Mouse, Rat samples. Cited in 1 publication. Immunogen corresponding to Recombinant Fragment Protein within Human DPYSL3 aa 100-250.
